
"remap escape key
noremap » <Esc>
inoremap » <Esc>
cnoremap » <Esc>
noremap <A-i> <Esc>
nnoremap <A-i> <Esc>
vnoremap <A-i> <Esc>
inoremap <A-i> <Esc>
cnoremap <A-i> <Esc>


" NEO arrow keys when in QWERTZ
"noremap € <Up>
"inoremap € <Up>
"cnoremap € <Up>
"noremap ð <Down>
"inoremap ð <Down>
"cnoremap ð <Down>
"noremap ſ <Left>
"inoremap ſ <Left>
"cnoremap ſ <Left>
"noremap đ <Right>
"inoremap đ <Right>
"cnoremap đ <Right>

" NEO move to eol / bol in QWERTZ
inoremap æ <C-a>
cnoremap æ <C-a>
inoremap ŋ <C-e>
cnoremap ŋ <C-e>

" forward / backword one word (emacs style)
inoremap <A-f> <C-Right>
cnoremap <A-f> <C-Right>
inoremap <A-b> <C-Left>
cnoremap <A-b> <C-Left>

" up and down in command history
cnoremap <C-p> <Up>
cnoremap <C-n> <Down>



"delete last word
inoremap <A-BS> <C-W>
cnoremap <A-BS> <C-W>

" switch tabs
noremap <A-p> :tabprevious<CR>
inoremap <A-p> <Esc>:tabprevious<CR>
noremap <A-n> :tabnext<CR>
inoremap <A-n> <Esc>:tabnext<CR>
" move tab 
noremap <A-S-p> i<C-S-PageUp>
noremap <A-S-n> i<C-S-PageDown>
" close tab
noremap <A-w> :tabclose<CR>
noremap d :tabclose<CR>

"move cursor
noremap <C-A-h> <left>
noremap <C-A-l> <right>

"delete last word
inoremap <S-Space> <C-BS>
cnoremap <S-Space> <C-W>

"scroll up and down
noremap <C-j> 5<down>
noremap <C-k> 5<up>
noremap <C-Space> <Space>
noremap <C-u> <S-Space>

" just to remember:
" M open message in new tag
" lr label as read





